Package org.jlibsedml.validation

Provides a collection of classes implementing ISedmlValidator that provide validation of SED-ML elements against the L1-V1 specification.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISedMLValidator
    Interface for different sorts of validation that can be performed on a SED-ML model or file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationValidator  
    AnnotationVisitorValidator  
    KisaoIDValidator
    Validates that the supplied KISAO id is a valid KISAO identifier.
    MathMLValidator
    Provides some validation that : An MathML element has its variables defined in ListOfVariables and ListOfParameters A node can be evaluated to a numerical value.
    ModelCyclesDetector
    Detects cycles in the source references of Model elements.
    RawContentsSchemaValidator
    Class responsible for validating a SED-ML file against its XML schema.
    SchematronValidator
    Validates against cross-references, model IDs and math statements using undeclared variables.
    SEDMLSchemaValidator
    Class responsible for validating a SED-ML model against its XML schema.
    URIValidator
    Validates that URIs in the 'source' attribute of a model can be parsed into URI objects.
    ValidatorController
    Access point to validators.

Package org.jlibsedml.validation Description

Provides a collection of classes implementing ISedmlValidator that provide validation of SED-ML elements against the L1-V1 specification.
